com.pega.pegarules.pub.reqres

Class ResponseOUT

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pega.pegarules.pub.reqres.ResponseOUT
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DefaultResponse, GenerateDDLResponse, HotFixResponse

    public abstract class ResponseOUT
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
     The Class ResponseOUT is the output entity that can be used CLI,UI and Service interfaces.
 Any operation that needs to be performed from CLI and Service can extend this class
 The corresponding request and response objects needs to be added in the ProcessorFactory
 {com.pega.pegarules.deploy.internal.processors.factory.ProcessorFactory#getResponse}
